 \"Just feel it, like someone who sprints 200m'.\\\"\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1354, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"200m\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hassan had initially signed up for the Olympic 1,500 metres as well before deciding that three events would be enough of a challenge.\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\", \"score\": 0.7704080584981509, \"rank\": 0.2965853070381443, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic 1,500 metres\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1415}, {\"ngram\": \"three events\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this week Hassan said that finishing the marathon is \\\"a kind of hell\\\", and on Sunday she collapsed after the finish line before picking herself up, beaming and waving as the crowd cheered.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1509, \"end\": 1515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\", \"score\": 0.7704080584981509, \"rank\": 0.2965853070381443, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the marathon\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"a kind\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"hell\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every step I challenged myself, and now I am so grateful I did not push myself too much on the track.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every step\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was scared of this race,\\\" she said afterwards.\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this race\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The race had been impossible to call with all the favourites among a leading pack up until the last 10km.\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The race\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1850}, {\"ngram\": \"all the favourites\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1902}, {\"ngram\": \"a leading pack\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"the last 10km\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Defending champion Kenya's Peres Jepchirchir then dropped back as Assefa ploughed ahead with a handful of challengers.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1968, \"end\": 1973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999999831743, \"rank\": 8.686675503972454e-12, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 1976, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peres_Jepchirchir\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Peres Jepchirchir\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peres_Jepchirchir\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peres_Jepchirchir\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"champion\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"Assefa\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2021}, {\"ngram\": \"a handful\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2051}, {\"ngram\": \"challengers\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hassan hung onto the back of the pack in much the same way she does on the track, biding her time before pouncing.\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2068, \"end\": 2074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\", \"score\": 0.7704080584981509, \"rank\": 0.2965853070381443, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"the pack\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2148}, {\"ngram\": \"her time\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She delivered her devastating turn of pace on the last turn, sneaking past Assefa on the inside and briefly knocking elbows with the Ethiopian, who tried to rally but could not catch up.\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2317, \"end\": 2326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\", \"score\": 0.9999734962145186, \"rank\": 2.6504487744380365e-05, \"text\": \"Ethiopian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her devastating turn\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2218}, {\"ngram\": \"pace\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"the last turn\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2243}, {\"ngram\": \"Assefa\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"the inside and briefly knocking elbows\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Assefa, 27, had looked likely to make it an Ethiopian sweep of the Olympic marathons after Tamirat Tola won the men's race on Saturday, as she surged up the course's steep hills looking calm and collected throughout.\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2463, \"end\": 2475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamirat_Tola\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tamirat Tola\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamirat_Tola\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamirat_Tola\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Assefa\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic marathons\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2456}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's race\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2506}, {\"ngram\": \"the course's steep hills\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Assefa has two of the fastest ever marathon times and took more than two minutes off the world record in a mixed race to win last year's Berlin marathon.\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2727, \"end\": 2742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin_Marathon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Berlin marathon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin_Marathon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Berlin_Marathon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Assefa\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2596}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest ever marathon times\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2639}, {\"ngram\": \"more than two minutes\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2670}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"a mixed race\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had to settle for silver on Sunday, though, in a repeat of her second-place finish at the London marathon in April when Jepchirchir prevailed.\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2891, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2839, \"end\": 2854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Marathon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"London marathon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Marathon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Marathon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2773}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2783}, {\"ngram\": \"a repeat\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2804}, {\"ngram\": \"her second-place finish\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2863}, {\"ngram\": \"Jepchirchir\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obiri, 34, ran a masterful race to clinch bronze, powering on despite having to stop and throw up at one point.\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 3004, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Obiri\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"a masterful race\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"one point\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3003}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt so bad in my stomach.\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my stomach\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know - maybe because of that, I stopped and puked,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then, to catch up with the girls, I used a lot of energy.\\\"\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3166, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the girls\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3154}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like Hassan, Obiri has added the 42km to her scintillating middle-distance career, having won silver in the 5,000m in Rio and Tokyo.\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3286, \"end\": 3289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6915971501198827e-17, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso